    <node id="Pipe Thread Tapping">
      <data key="d0">Pipe Thread Tapping</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Pipe Thread Tapping refers to the process of creating threaded holes in pipe fittings, requiring sufficient metal thickness or reinforcement with a boss.</data>
