    <node id="Butt Welding">
      <data key="d0">Butt Welding</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Butt Welding is a method of directly attaching connections to the wall of a fitting, with reinforcement requirements for openings.&lt;SEP&gt;Butt Welding is a technique for connecting pipes, referenced in Fig. 14 of the ASME B16.5-2013 document.</data>
