      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Hub Diameter represents a dimensional specification for flanges, varying by pipe size.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub Diameter refers to the minimum diameter of the hub in Class 600 Flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub Diameter refers to a critical dimension specified in the technical standard for flange specifications.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4303e33e6d61d4207aeb4ef2e5ef35ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1359b097a2ba15f87aae6ad689a2a7a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90c280892e81306b9d7b1a397e54f308</data>
