      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">American War Standard B16e5-1943 is a wartime-specific standard published for pressure–temperature ratings of materials and pressure classes.&lt;SEP&gt;American War Standard B16e5-1943 is a wartime revision of pressure–temperature ratings for flanges and fittings.</data>
