    <node id="Mandatory Appendix II">
      <data key="d0">Mandatory Appendix II</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Mandatory Appendix II is a section of the ASME B16.5-2013 standard that serves as a supplementary document containing detailed technical specifications and referenced figures. It provides dimensional data primarily in inch units for flanges and fittings, including specific figures and tables related to flange dimensions, bolting requirements, and gasket specifications. The appendix is explicitly cited in the standard’s text for critical details such as ring joint facing dimensions and other engineering parameters. Notably, it includes Table II-22, which outlines inch-based dimensions for Class 150 flanges, a key component of the standard. While some descriptions emphasize its role in housing flange-specific data, others highlight its broader function in referencing technical specifications across engineering contexts. The content is integral to ensuring compliance with dimensional standards for pipe fittings and flanges in industrial applications.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d361c91bf3e9c4f81478ff64f43f6fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b181980b1dcef22dc859d6b6b9c724e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6189c0e80ab7926dfac81b4ef4dc7737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-baede3ecfe2637d28f283b80b0cc9cf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a0311f8fc78c3478b577229218993&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce8d00c0b7f9fa8976b26a74e2c65e04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43e5005d4928be252c7355587c71a1aa</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776334533</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="ASME International">
      <data key="d0">ASME International</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME International is the copyright holder of numerous technical standards and documents, including the ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code, material specifications standards, and the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, which provides technical specifications for pipe flanges and fittings, as well as pressure-temperature ratings. The organization oversees the publication and distribution of these standards, often licensing their use through entities like IHS. It is also associated with cosponsoring committees such as the B16 Committee and holds copyright for technical documentation related to flanged fittings. ASME International functions as a licensing organization for its standards, ensuring controlled distribution and providing content under license agreements. Its role includes managing technical specifications within documents and acting as a key authority in the development and maintenance of industry-related standards.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0f2fde18096ae54093e820b71568eac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83d5456d4c5892bce6dfc092c06f75b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1261f13c12701dc16f49237f702e1cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d361c91bf3e9c4f81478ff64f43f6fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c0c6be7420f2242b28a9c7ea1e74ab1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f5dfdb3c7a4f92fcc61b0351584206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8f5c9d7666d5ca64fad9fe5409f4a67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d82012bf555fc35faff1378794cfede8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-335c2335ba413830aae1a70244aa5a26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b3edae33580408b591d5cc7c7743878&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9866fd2e84ba4e57228a299a787a799b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88c25523fb6a395eb9e2724eb0719d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ab283e30659c933554a033613d2618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da1dc127b60347090430c8c8af38fef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84025523a525583a26ec2f8f36a4686c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8d7fbf71d349a93ea469c5166b31e89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2aa51a49817516d8e488a9d7c544a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1359b097a2ba15f87aae6ad689a2a7a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe557ad0e335444e461df848f9e28d6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd6664ea75cb381eb0927fcbdada5e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6189c0e80ab7926dfac81b4ef4dc7737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71a674a140c79338fd271bcee63fa8e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f17e2ea5f154e082324b9ac9b148a73e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f59cecabea5b953c2fb1a5d4e4c62175&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2879e8ce1f305f975a2bf33f2d701842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10c30ffd05f9872afae7074e64385b46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-745a7a353b1e1e00489d9e9aa987acd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2862b7e64a5fd03e51c5fca146576eec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30fa107e1afe5b6cba81caa3af7a1ab4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5ace9ce39146c54679f4e19c3434a59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43e5005d4928be252c7355587c71a1aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5ad05cffa1690c182bd060ab81bc6ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d0f7d26ba441435e49ef6d46820f716&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-366d21bccd71c76a4c780fde0cfa7e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f58e723d717e78901685416a73eb271b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac011d5da9f248ab56440661b906cb38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c020691beabe3e74dfac9d5fd0420b2</data>
