    <node id="ASME B16.5-2013">
      <data key="d0">ASME B16.5-2013</data>
      <data key="d1">standard</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME B16.5-2013 is a technical standard governing specifications for pipe flanges and flanged fittings, covering nominal pipe sizes (NPS) 1/2 through NPS 24 in both metric and inch systems. It serves as a revision of the 2009 edition and outlines dimensional requirements, including facing types (e.g., Ring-Joint Facings), drilling templates, and tolerances for welding ends. The standard addresses material requirements, pressure-temperature ratings for specific material groups (such as Group 2.12, 2.4, and 2.5), and guidelines for flange bolting and gasket compatibility. It includes specifications for multiple pressure rating classes, such as Class 150, 300, 400, 600, 900, 1500, and 2500, with detailed dimensional data for each. Additionally, it references other standards like ASME B1.20.1 and contains nonmandatory appendices, such as Appendix C, which provide supplementary information. The document also defines methods for pressure-temperature ratings, material classifications, and permissible imperfections in flanges, ensuring consistency and safety in piping systems.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44664e1f68bc892f4b7b0a535c4414b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0f2fde18096ae54093e820b71568eac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09c7747fb737fd6e9b29eb11eb4c7556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83d5456d4c5892bce6dfc092c06f75b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02c8f43c223cee2154c66d0d4ab324af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccbc09bef8fd93e5314dec1dbec481cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1261f13c12701dc16f49237f702e1cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c0c6be7420f2242b28a9c7ea1e74ab1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f58e723d717e78901685416a73eb271b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f5dfdb3c7a4f92fcc61b0351584206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-376c9d90c67ab8cb5f4d7bef0d9995e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8f5c9d7666d5ca64fad9fe5409f4a67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d82012bf555fc35faff1378794cfede8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-439097792cec97ce9b1b0fb080fa39fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-335c2335ba413830aae1a70244aa5a26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc4f25f5a21132e1571d8baa298136c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-157dd67058da951e9c5cc75c8d297ca5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4303e33e6d61d4207aeb4ef2e5ef35ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88c25523fb6a395eb9e2724eb0719d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ab283e30659c933554a033613d2618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da1dc127b60347090430c8c8af38fef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84025523a525583a26ec2f8f36a4686c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8d7fbf71d349a93ea469c5166b31e89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2aa51a49817516d8e488a9d7c544a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-925b39d264b455e6e2dfa9b4a8725e96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1359b097a2ba15f87aae6ad689a2a7a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5ae20c528cd11f1deab499df53ad378&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f024c3dde67312e25d76e977dcb7753c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd6664ea75cb381eb0927fcbdada5e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab03fc59cd1984b5768de1c8c3e1f065&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6189c0e80ab7926dfac81b4ef4dc7737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4acf0f73e6504183b866c554db452bae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71a674a140c79338fd271bcee63fa8e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30dae618425190cfb2b37b3fc339e4ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c20399bbbf3