    <node id="IHS">
      <data key="d0">IHS</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">IHS is an organization licensed by ASME International to distribute technical standards and provide access to its content under specific terms. It operates as a third-party provider authorized to share ASME standards, including the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, which outlines specifications for pipe flanges and flanged fittings. This licensing agreement restricts unauthorized reproduction, resale, and networking of the distributed materials. IHS enforces these limitations to ensure compliance with ASME International's intellectual property policies, prohibiting users from copying, modifying, or redistributing the technical documents without explicit permission. The organization's role involves acting as an intermediary between ASME International and end-users, offering access to a range of technical content while adhering to the licensing conditions set by the original copyright holder. Multiple descriptions emphasize IHS's function in providing standardized technical information under legal agreements, highlighting its responsibility to maintain the integrity and proper usage of ASME's published works.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0f2fde18096ae54093e820b71568eac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83d5456d4c5892bce6dfc092c06f75b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1261f13c12701dc16f49237f702e1cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d361c91bf3e9c4f81478ff64f43f6fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c0c6be7420f2242b28a9c7ea1e74ab1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f5dfdb3c7a4f92fcc61b0351584206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8f5c9d7666d5ca64fad9fe5409f4a67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d82012bf555fc35faff1378794cfede8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-335c2335ba413830aae1a70244aa5a26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9866fd2e84ba4e57228a299a787a799b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88c25523fb6a395eb9e2724eb0719d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ab283e30659c933554a033613d2618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da1dc127b60347090430c8c8af38fef9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84025523a525583a26ec2f8f36a4686c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8d7fbf71d349a93ea469c5166b31e89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2aa51a49817516d8e488a9d7c544a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1359b097a2ba15f87aae6ad689a2a7a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe557ad0e335444e461df848f9e28d6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd6664ea75cb381eb0927fcbdada5e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab03fc59cd1984b5768de1c8c3e1f065&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6189c0e80ab7926dfac81b4ef4dc7737&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71a674a140c79338fd271bcee63fa8e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f17e2ea5f154e082324b9ac9b148a73e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2879e8ce1f305f975a2bf33f2d701842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10c30ffd05f9872afae7074e64385b46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5fd12d8684f80d487e4f8acfca82848a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-745a7a353b1e1e00489d9e9aa987acd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2862b7e64a5fd03e51c5fca146576eec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30fa107e1afe5b6cba81caa3af7a1ab4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5ace9ce39146c54679f4e19c3434a59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce8d00c0b7f9fa8976b26a74e2c65e04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43e5005d4928be252c7355587c71a1aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5ad05cffa1690c182bd060ab81bc6ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d0f7d26ba441435e49ef6d46820f716&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-366d21bccd71c