    <node id="A182 Gr. F12">
      <data key="d0">A182 Gr. F12</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c38d97b0aceca7464ebbbd9a7db0c8d9</data>
      <data key="d2">A182 Gr. F12 is associated with the Pressure–Temperature Ratings table." But the original text lists different materials with their own pressure ratings. So each material (A182 Gr. F12, 5Cr–1⁄2Mo, A182 Gr. F92) should have a relationship with the Pressure–Temperature Ratings table. However, in the previous output, only A182 Gr. F12 was linked. The other materials (5Cr–1⁄2Mo and A182 Gr. F92) might have been missed in the relationships.</data>
      <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776334552</data>
      <data key="d6" />
